title: UDEMY LEARN WORDPRESS 4 FROM SCRATCH CREATE AWESOME WEBSITES TUT
description:
This course on latest Wordpress Release Version 4.2.4
is developed keeping in mind the people who have
no prior knowledge of Web Development and so this
course helps you understand the Wordpress Basics
in great details so that you can create websites
using Wordpress with ease without writing any
code

This course is different from other courses as it not only teaches
you basics but also helps you in creating your first
responsive website for your business or for your personal blog

This course covers everything from very basics so that you can
practice along the lectures
